---
title: Nintendo Switch Daily Usage and Advanced Configuration
---

graph TD
    %% Daily Usage Entry
    DAILY_START([Daily Switch Usage]) --> USAGE_TYPE{Select Activity}

    USAGE_TYPE -->|Boot Console| BOOT_PROCESS[Console Boot Process]
    USAGE_TYPE -->|Install Games| GAME_INSTALL[Game Installation]
    USAGE_TYPE -->|Manage Saves| SAVE_MANAGEMENT[Save Management]
    USAGE_TYPE -->|Homebrew Access| HOMEBREW_ACCESS[Homebrew Applications]
    USAGE_TYPE -->|System Maintenance| MAINTENANCE[System Maintenance]

    %% Boot Process Flow
    BOOT_PROCESS --> CONSOLE_TYPE{Console Type}
    CONSOLE_TYPE -->|RCM Method| RCM_BOOT[RCM Boot Process]
    CONSOLE_TYPE -->|Modchip| MODCHIP_BOOT[Modchip Auto-Boot]

    RCM_BOOT --> POWER_ON[Power On Console]
    POWER_ON --> ENTER_RCM[Enter RCM Mode<br/>Jig + Power + Vol+]
    ENTER_RCM --> INJECT_PAYLOAD[Inject Payload<br/>Hekate/KEFIR]
    INJECT_PAYLOAD --> SELECT_BOOT[Select Boot Option]

    MODCHIP_BOOT --> MODCHIP_POWER[Power On Normally]
    MODCHIP_POWER --> AUTO_LAUNCH[Auto-Launch to Menu]
    AUTO_LAUNCH --> SELECT_BOOT

    SELECT_BOOT --> BOOT_CHOICE{Choose Environment}
    BOOT_CHOICE -->|SysNAND Stock| STOCK_BOOT[Official Firmware<br/>Online Safe]
    BOOT_CHOICE -->|SysNAND CFW| SYSNAND_CFW[CFW on Internal<br/>Homebrew Access]
    BOOT_CHOICE -->|EmuNAND| EMUNAND_BOOT[EmuNAND Environment<br/>Piracy Safe]

    %% Game Installation Flow
    GAME_INSTALL --> INSTALL_SOURCE{Installation Source}
    INSTALL_SOURCE -->|Local Files| LOCAL_INSTALL[Local Installation]
    INSTALL_SOURCE -->|Network| NETWORK_INSTALL[Network Installation]

    LOCAL_INSTALL --> DBI_LOCAL[Launch DBI]
    DBI_LOCAL --> SELECT_FILES[Select Game Files<br/>NSP/XCI]
    SELECT_FILES --> CHOOSE_LOCATION[Choose Install Location<br/>SD/Internal]
    CHOOSE_LOCATION --> INSTALL_EXECUTE[Execute Installation]

    NETWORK_INSTALL --> DBI_NETWORK[DBI Network Install]
    DBI_NETWORK --> CONNECT_SOURCE[Connect to Source<br/>PC/FTP/HTTP]
    CONNECT_SOURCE --> BROWSE_GAMES[Browse Game Library]
    BROWSE_GAMES --> INSTALL_EXECUTE

    INSTALL_EXECUTE --> VERIFY_INSTALL[Verify Installation]
    VERIFY_INSTALL --> INSTALL_COMPLETE[✅ Game Installed]

    %% Save Management Flow
    SAVE_MANAGEMENT --> SAVE_ACTION{Save Action}
    SAVE_ACTION -->|Backup Saves| BACKUP_SAVES[Backup Process]
    SAVE_ACTION -->|Restore Saves| RESTORE_SAVES[Restore Process]
    SAVE_ACTION -->|Transfer Saves| TRANSFER_SAVES[Transfer Process]

    BACKUP_SAVES --> LAUNCH_JKSV[Launch JKSV/Checkpoint]
    LAUNCH_JKSV --> SELECT_GAME[Select Game]
    SELECT_GAME --> EXPORT_SAVE[Export Save Data]
    EXPORT_SAVE --> SAVE_LOCATION[Choose Save Location<br/>SD/PC]
    SAVE_LOCATION --> BACKUP_COMPLETE[✅ Backup Complete]

    RESTORE_SAVES --> LAUNCH_JKSV
    SELECT_GAME --> IMPORT_SAVE[Import Save Data]
    IMPORT_SAVE --> SELECT_BACKUP[Select Backup File]
    SELECT_BACKUP --> RESTORE_COMPLETE[✅ Restore Complete]

    %% Homebrew Access Flow
    HOMEBREW_ACCESS --> HOMEBREW_METHOD{Access Method}
    HOMEBREW_METHOD -->|Album Method| ALBUM_ACCESS[Hold L + Open Album]
    HOMEBREW_METHOD -->|Tesla Overlay| TESLA_ACCESS[Hold L + R In-Game]
    HOMEBREW_METHOD -->|Direct Launch| DIRECT_LAUNCH[Launch from Home]

    ALBUM_ACCESS --> HOMEBREW_MENU[Homebrew Launcher]
    TESLA_ACCESS --> OVERLAY_MENU[Tesla Overlay Menu]
    DIRECT_LAUNCH --> SPECIFIC_APP[Specific Homebrew App]

    HOMEBREW_MENU --> APP_SELECTION[Select Application]
    OVERLAY_MENU --> OVERLAY_FUNCTION[Select Overlay Function]
    APP_SELECTION --> APP_LAUNCH[Launch Selected App]
    OVERLAY_FUNCTION --> FEATURE_USE[Use Feature]

    %% System Maintenance Flow
    MAINTENANCE --> MAINTENANCE_TYPE{Maintenance Task}
    MAINTENANCE_TYPE -->|Update CFW| UPDATE_CFW[Update Custom Firmware]
    MAINTENANCE_TYPE -->|Clean System| CLEAN_SYSTEM[System Cleanup]
    MAINTENANCE_TYPE -->|Check Health| SYSTEM_HEALTH[System Health Check]

    UPDATE_CFW --> DOWNLOAD_KEFIR[Download Latest KEFIR]
    DOWNLOAD_KEFIR --> BACKUP_CURRENT[Backup Current Setup]
    BACKUP_CURRENT --> INSTALL_UPDATE[Install Updated CFW]
    INSTALL_UPDATE --> TEST_BOOT[Test Boot Process]
    TEST_BOOT --> CFW_UPDATED[✅ CFW Updated]

    CLEAN_SYSTEM --> CLEAR_CACHE[Clear System Cache]
    CLEAR_CACHE --> ORGANIZE_FILES[Organize SD Card Files]
    ORGANIZE_FILES --> CHECK_SPACE[Check Storage Space]
    CHECK_SPACE --> CLEANUP_COMPLETE[✅ Cleanup Complete]

    SYSTEM_HEALTH --> CHECK_SD[Check SD Card Health]
    CHECK_SD --> VERIFY_BACKUPS[Verify Backup Integrity]
    VERIFY_BACKUPS --> TEST_FUNCTIONS[Test Key Functions]
    TEST_FUNCTIONS --> HEALTH_REPORT[Generate Health Report]

    %% Advanced Configuration
    ADVANCED_CONFIG([Advanced Configuration]) --> CONFIG_TYPE{Configuration Type}
    CONFIG_TYPE -->|Overclocking| OVERCLOCK_SETUP[Overclocking Setup]
    CONFIG_TYPE -->|Theme/Mods| THEME_SETUP[Theme and Mods]
    CONFIG_TYPE -->|Network Config| NETWORK_SETUP[Network Configuration]
    CONFIG_TYPE -->|Security Config| SECURITY_SETUP[Security Configuration]

    %% Overclocking Flow
    OVERCLOCK_SETUP --> SYSCLK_INSTALL[Install sys-clk Module]
    SYSCLK_INSTALL --> OC_CONFIGURE[Configure Overclock Profiles]
    OC_CONFIGURE --> OC_WARNING{Stability Warning}
    OC_WARNING -->|Accept Risk| OC_ENABLE[Enable Overclocking]
    OC_WARNING -->|Too Risky| OC_SKIP[Skip Overclocking]
    OC_ENABLE --> OC_TEST[Test Stability]
    OC_TEST --> OC_COMPLETE[✅ Overclocking Active]

    %% Network Configuration
    NETWORK_SETUP --> DNS_CONFIG[Configure DNS Settings]
    DNS_CONFIG --> DNS_TYPE{DNS Purpose}
    DNS_TYPE -->|Block Nintendo| SET_90DNS[Set 90DNS<br/>163.172.141.219]
    DNS_TYPE -->|Allow Nintendo| CLEAR_DNS[Clear DNS/Use Auto]
    SET_90DNS --> TEST_BLOCKING[Test Server Blocking]
    CLEAR_DNS --> TEST_ONLINE[Test Online Access]
    TEST_BLOCKING --> NETWORK_COMPLETE[✅ Network Configured]
    TEST_ONLINE --> NETWORK_COMPLETE

    %% Final Success States
    STOCK_BOOT --> USAGE_SUCCESS[✅ Ready for Use]
    SYSNAND_CFW --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    EMUNAND_BOOT --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    INSTALL_COMPLETE --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    BACKUP_COMPLETE --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    RESTORE_COMPLETE --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    APP_LAUNCH --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    FEATURE_USE --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    CFW_UPDATED --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    CLEANUP_COMPLETE --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    HEALTH_REPORT --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    OC_COMPLETE --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    OC_SKIP --> USAGE_SUCCESS
    NETWORK_COMPLETE --> USAGE_SUCCESS

